{
  "stem": "734.5",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he said to me, [PAUSES FOR 9 SECONDS] you are free now.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] And I said something in French, [FRENCH].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And everybody started screaming, [FRENCH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And there must have been several hundred people at the gate.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I mean, the emotion was just hard to, to recall.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But it was hard to believe that this is possible, that we are really free.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[SOBBING] If we could only get to-- I mean, I cannot tell you what it was like to see those, to see those tanks, full of mud.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "If we could only get to them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I mean, I'm sure everybody was ready to kiss them, to, to embrace them, to fall right over them.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I-- people who haven't been able to move, sick people crawled on their bellies to the gate to see those tanks.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It was like absolutely-- what a scene that was.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Just, awful-- I mean, not awful in the sense that-- it was simply an unbelievable scene.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "[SOBBING] I'll never forget what this meant to us, to be free again.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "It was something we, we were waiting for six years.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Suddenly, this smudged face on a tank says that you are free now.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I, I didn't know the word free.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But I knew what he meant.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I said, [FRENCH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And this is really what he meant.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "This was really what the whole thing meant all about-- what the whole thing was about, to be free again.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And it was just a indescribable moment I ever witnessed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I don't think I ever-- I think this is about the first time I talk about it.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
